00:37:32.458 --> 00:37:33.417
SEOUL MILK

00:37:39.590 --> 00:37:41.634
-Watch it.
-I'm sorry, sir.

00:37:41.717 --> 00:37:43.302
-I'm sorry.
-You should be careful.

00:37:43.386 --> 00:37:45.221
-What is it, Dad?
-Are you okay?

00:37:45.304 --> 00:37:46.973
-Yes.
-You…

00:37:54.230 --> 00:37:55.606
The kid's not to blame.

00:37:56.315 --> 00:37:58.234
If you don't study,
that'll be your future.

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:05.283
It just had to be a day
when I had math class.

00:38:06.450 --> 00:38:09.745
Math classes were split
according to your grades.

00:38:09.829 --> 00:38:12.581
I was in the A class, so naturally,

00:38:12.665 --> 00:38:14.375
Cheon Sang-yeon was too.

